text: Kampong Mendaram Besar (Malay for Mendaram Besar Village) is a village in Belait District, Brunei, within the mukim of Labi. The postcode for Kampong Mendaram Besar is KE3537. == See also == * List of villages in Brunei * Kampong Mendaram Kecil == References == Mendaram Besar
title: Kampong Mendaram Besar
